**Impact:** `UnderscoreRegex1/2/3` at L36-38 are always compiled even on .NET 7+ where the other regexes use `[GeneratedRegex]`. These should also get source-generated equivalents.  
**Files:** CaseTransformExtensions.cs:L36-38  
